Comcast has been providing cable television service to Davis area residents for awhile, and now offers broadband internet service in Davis as well.  The base price for broadband internet and basic cable TV service is about $57 per month, though they have been offering various discounts to entice customers away from existing options such as ["SBC Global"] and ["Omsoft"].
